      h3.govuk-heading-m Third-party websites

      p.govuk-body DCMS does not take responsibility for any cookies placed on your device from other websites. Please note that if you click through to a website that we have provided a link to, DCMS has no control over the cookies set on these websites, so please see that organisations cookie policy and setting pages for details on how to manage their cookies.
